    "answer_id" : 1877609,
    "question_id" : 1873995,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>What I do with my TestNG, (sorry, JUnit doesn't support this) test cases is I can assign a group to the test I want to run</p>\n\n<pre><code>@Test(groups=\"broken\")\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>And then simply run 'mvn -Dgroups=broken'.</p>\n"
