    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>New versions of JUnit contains the Categories runner:\n<a href=\"http://kentbeck.github.com/junit/doc/ReleaseNotes4.8.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">http://kentbeck.github.com/junit/doc/ReleaseNotes4.8.html</a></p>\n\n<p>But releasing procedure of JUnit is not maven based, so maven users have to put it manually to their repositories.</p>\n"
