      "body" : "I got <code>No Tests Were Executed !</code> too, because i have <code>jUnit</code> and <code>TestNg</code> together in maven project dependencies. Removing <code>TestNg</code> or changing <code>@Test</code> annotation to <code>@org.testng.annotations.Test</code> solved problem for me."
