      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 0,
      "profile_image" : "https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-AqTumlgrdcA/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAEY/BMldnFss8Kw/s256-rj/photo.jpg",
      "display_name" : "Nazmul Hoque Shafin",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/4325630/nazmul-hoque-shafin"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 14,
    "last_activity_date" : 1530501008,
    "creation_date" : 1530501008,
    "answer_id" : 51128689,
    "question_id" : 1873995,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can run specific test class(es) and method(s) using the following syntax:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <ol>\n  <li><p>full package : mvn test -Dtest=\"com.oracle.tests.**\"</p></li>\n  <li><p>all method in a class : mvn test -Dtest=CLASS_NAME1</p></li>\n  <li><p>single method from single class :mvn test -Dtest=CLASS_NAME1#METHOD_NAME1</p></li>\n  <li><p>multiple method from multiple class : mvn test -Dtest=CLASS_NAME1#METHOD_NAME1,CLASS_NAME2#METHOD_NAME2</p></li>\n  </ol>\n</blockquote>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 5810084,
      "reputation" : 41,
      "user_id" : 4581466,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/45ea324c31894b18b2e6fda6b1cd4fcf?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "bsk",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/4581466/bsk"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 4,
    "last_activity_date" : 1541641548,
    "creation_date" : 1541641548,
    "answer_id" : 53200418,
    "question_id" : 1873995,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As of surefire plugin version 2.22.1 (possibly earlier) you can run single test using testnames property when using testng.xml</p>\n\n<p>Given a following testng.xml</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;\n&lt;!DOCTYPE suite SYSTEM \"http://testng.org/testng-1.0.dtd\"&gt;\n&lt;suite name=\"Suite\"&gt;\n    &lt;test name=\"all-tests\"&gt;\n        &lt;classes&gt;\n            &lt;class name=\"server.Atest\"/&gt;\n            &lt;class name=\"server.Btest\"/&gt;\n            &lt;class name=\"server.Ctest\"/&gt;\n        &lt;/classes&gt;\n    &lt;/test&gt;\n    &lt;test name=\"run-A-test\"&gt;\n        &lt;classes&gt;\n            &lt;class name=\"server.Atest\"/&gt;\n        &lt;/classes&gt;\n    &lt;/test&gt;\n    &lt;test name=\"run-B-test\"&gt;\n        &lt;classes&gt;\n            &lt;class name=\"server.Btest\"/&gt;\n        &lt;/classes&gt;\n    &lt;/test&gt;\n    &lt;test name=\"run-C-test\"&gt;\n        &lt;classes&gt;\n            &lt;class name=\"server.Ctest\"/&gt;\n        &lt;/classes&gt;\n    &lt;/test&gt;\n&lt;/suite&gt; \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>with the pom.xml</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;\n&lt;project xmlns=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\" xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd\"&gt;\n    &lt;modelVersion&gt;4.0.0&lt;/modelVersion&gt;\n    [...]\n    &lt;properties&gt;\n        &lt;selectedTests&gt;all-tests&lt;/selectedTests&gt;\n    &lt;/properties&gt;\n    [...]\n    &lt;plugins&gt;\n        &lt;plugin&gt;\n            &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n            &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-surefire-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n            &lt;version&gt;2.22.1&lt;/version&gt;\n            &lt;configuration&gt;\n                &lt;suiteXmlFiles&gt;\n                    &lt;file&gt;src/test/resources/testng.xml&lt;/file&gt;\n                &lt;/suiteXmlFiles&gt;\n                &lt;properties&gt;\n                    &lt;property&gt;\n                        &lt;name&gt;testnames&lt;/name&gt;\n                        &lt;value&gt;${selectedTests}&lt;/value&gt;\n                    &lt;/property&gt;\n                &lt;/properties&gt;\n            &lt;/configuration&gt;\n        &lt;/plugin&gt;\n    &lt;/plugins&gt;\n    [...]\n&lt;/project&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>From command line</p>\n\n<pre><code>mvn clean test -DselectedTests=run-B-test\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Further reading - <a href=\"http://maven.apache.org/surefire/maven-surefire-plugin/examples/testng.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Maven surefire plugin using testng</a></p>\n"
  }, {
