    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<h1>Run a single test method from a test class.</h1>\n<p><code>mvn test -Dtest=Test1#methodname</code></p>\n<hr />\n<h1>Other related use-cases</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><p><code>mvn test // Run all the unit test classes</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>mvn test -Dtest=Test1 // Run a single test class</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>mvn test -Dtest=Test1,Test2 // Run multiple test classes</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>mvn test -Dtest=Test1#testFoo* // Run all test methods that match pattern 'testFoo*' from a test class.</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>mvn test -Dtest=Test1#testFoo*+testBar* // Run all test methods match pattern 'testFoo*' and 'testBar*' from a test class.</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"
