    "question_id" : 1873995,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You need to specify the JUnit test class and its method to be executed.</p>\n<pre><code>mvn test -Dtest=com.mycompany.AppTest#testMethod\n</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://metamug.com/article/java/build-run-java-maven-project-command-line.html#running-unit-tests\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://metamug.com/article/java/build-run-java-maven-project-command-line.html#running-unit-tests</a></p>\n"
